text: Sir George Gunning, 2nd Baronet (1763–1823), of Horton, Northamptonshire, was an English politician. He was a Member of Parliament (MP) for Wigan 21 June 1800 – 1802, Hastings 1802 – 1806 and East Grinstead 9 March 1812 – May 1812 and 1812 – 1818.http://www.historyofparliamentonline.org/volume/1790-1820/member/gunning- george-william-1763-1823 ==References== Category:Baronets in the Baronetage of England Category:People from South Northamptonshire District Category:1763 births Category:1823 deaths Category:Politicians from Northamptonshire Category:Members of the Parliament of Great Britain for English constituencies Category:British MPs 1796–1800 Category:UK MPs 1801–1802 Category:UK MPs 1802–1806 Category:UK MPs 1807–1812 Category:UK MPs 1812–1818 Category:Members of the Parliament of the United Kingdom for English constituencies
